3181_cover-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/67bf00ebbbdd0128f5063181_cover-p-800.png 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/67bf00ebbbdd0128f5063181_cover-p-1080.png 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/67bf00ebbbdd0128f5063181_cover.png 1280w" class="blog-card-img"/></div><strong class="blog-card-title">UX Writing Best Practices: Lessons from the Field</strong><p class="blog-card-text">From Reddit wisdom to our real design experience, this guide dives into UX writing best practices that actually work — with tips, examples, and common pitfalls.</p></a></div></div></div></div></div></main><footer class="main-footer-2"><div class="main-footer__container main-footer__container--sm"><div class="main-footer__wrapper"><div class="main-footer__left"><div class="main-footer__left-wrap"><a aria-label="main page" href="../index.html" class="main-footer__logo w-inline-block"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/5e8b46679e241c5d4b095331_logo.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="main-footer__logo-img"/></a><address class="main-footer__address"><p class="main-footer__address-text">Kyiv, Ukraine, <br/></p><p class="main-footer__address-text d-sm-block">Dehtiarivska str. 33B </p></address></div><div class="main-footer__left-wrap"><address class="main-footer__address"><p class="main-footer__address-text">Eleken Design Ltd<br/></p><p class="main-footer__address-text">920-736 Granville ST<br/></p><p class="main-footer__address-text">Vancouver BC V6Z 1G3<br/></p><p class="main-footer__address-text">Canada<br/></p></address></div></div><div class="main-footer__right"><div class="main-footer__row"><div class="main-footer__col d-sm-none"><div class="main-footer__wrap-list-title"><div class="main-footer__list-title"><strong class="bold-text-10">Services</strong></div><div class="main-footer__list-title-decor"></div></div><ul role="list" class="main-footer__list 